{"title":"docker安装kafka","date":"2020-05-07T19:01:58.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 8, 2020","L":"05/08/2020","MM-DD":"05-08"},"link":"2020/05/08/docker-install-kafka","tags":["docker","kafka"],"categories":["kafka"],"updated":"2020-05-12T08:08:33.718Z","content":"<h2 id=\"kafka\">kafka<a title=\"#kafka\" href=\"#kafka\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"下载zookeeper镜像\">下载zookeeper镜像<a title=\"#下载zookeeper镜像\" href=\"#下载zookeeper镜像\"></a></h3>\n<p>kafka需要zookeeper管理，所以需要先安装zookeeper。可以下载官方的<code>zookeeper</code>或者<code>wurstmeister/zookeeper</code>版本，建议下载<code>wurstmeister/zookeeper</code>，kafka也是选择的<code>wurstmeister/kafka</code>版本</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull zookeeper:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>or</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull wurstmeister/zookeeper:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行zookeeper容器\">运行zookeeper容器<a title=\"#运行zookeeper容器\" href=\"#运行zookeeper容器\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run --name zookeeper -p 2181:2181 -d zookeeper</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>or</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run --name zookeeper -p 2181:2181 -d wurstmeister/zookeeper</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"下载kafka镜像\">下载kafka镜像<a title=\"#下载kafka镜像\" href=\"#下载kafka镜像\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull wurstmeister/kafka:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行kafka容器\">运行kafka容器<a title=\"#运行kafka容器\" href=\"#运行kafka容器\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run  -d --name kafka -p 9092:9092 -e KAFKA_BROKER_ID=0 -e KAFKA_ZOOKEEPER_CONNECT=192.168.222.133:2181 -e KAFKA_ADVERTISED_LISTENERS=PLAINTEXT://192.168.222.133:9092 -e KAFKA_LISTENERS=PLAINTEXT://0.0.0.0:9092 -t wurstmeister/kafka</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>这里主要设置4个参数<br>\n<code>-e KAFKA_BROKER_ID=0</code> 在kafka集群中，每个kafka都有一个BROKER_ID来区分自己<br>\n<code>-e KAFKA_ZOOKEEPER_CONNECT=192.168.222.133:2181/kafka</code> 配置zookeeper管理kafka的路径<br>\n<code>-e KAFKA_ADVERTISED_LISTENERS=PLAINTEXT://192.168.222.133:9092</code> 把kafka的地址端口注册给zookeeper<br>\n<code>-e KAFKA_LISTENERS=PLAINTEXT://0.0.0.0:9092</code> 配置kafka的监听端口</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>第2点和第3点的ip换成服务器ip<br>\n代码后面还可以加上<code>-v /etc/localtime:/etc/localtime</code>用于指定容器时间同步虚拟机的时间</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"kafka管理器\">kafka管理器<a title=\"#kafka管理器\" href=\"#kafka管理器\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"安装kafka-manager\">安装kafka-manager<a title=\"#安装kafka-manager\" href=\"#安装kafka-manager\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull sheepkiller/kafka-manager:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行kafka-manager\">运行kafka-manager<a title=\"#运行kafka-manager\" href=\"#运行kafka-manager\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run -d --name kafka-manager \\--link zookeeper:zookeeper \\--link kafka:kafka -p 9000:9000 \\--restart=always \\--env ZK_HOSTS=zookeeper:2181 \\</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","next":{"title":"世界上的另一个我","link":"2020/04/29/another-me-in-the-world"},"plink":"http://blog.arytry.com/2020/05/08/docker-install-kafka/","toc":[{"id":"kafka","title":"kafka","index":"1","children":[{"id":"下载zookeeper镜像","title":"下载zookeeper镜像","index":"1.1"},{"id":"运行zookeeper容器","title":"运行zookeeper容器","index":"1.2"},{"id":"下载kafka镜像","title":"下载kafka镜像","index":"1.3"},{"id":"运行kafka容器","title":"运行kafka容器","index":"1.4"}]},{"id":"kafka管理器","title":"kafka管理器","index":"2","children":[{"id":"安装kafka-manager","title":"安装kafka-manager","index":"2.1"},{"id":"运行kafka-manager","title":"运行kafka-manager","index":"2.2"}]}],"reward":true}